headline.main: Tobacco Road Intersects Flatbush Avenue as ACC Comes to NYC
headline.print_headline: Tobacco Road Intersects Flatbush Avenue as ACC Comes to NYC

lead_paragraph: Tobacco Road intersects with Flatbush Avenue this week when the Atlantic Coast Conference Tournament comes to the Barclays Center in Brooklyn.
